Items.c: <[>接下來...去點燃三個有黑衣人把守的燈檯,就能打開機關門進入水道深處,搶人寶物的黑衣人就在那裡。<]>
Items.mt: <[>Next... Go and light up the three light tables guarded by the men in black, and you will be able to open the door to the deeper part of the waterway, where the men in black who robbed people of their treasures are. <]>
